James M. Lapeyre Jr.Founder and President, Laitram L.L.C.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 3 different industries.See Board Relationships64--
Background

		Mr. James M. Lapeyre, Jr., also known as Jay, has been the President of Laitram L.L.C. ('Laitram') and its predecessors since 1989. Mr. Lapeyre founded Laitram L.L.C. He has been the Chairman of the Board at ION Geophysical Corporation (formerly Input/Output Inc.) since January 1, 2013. He served as the Chairman of ION Geophysical Corporation from 1999 to January 1, 2012. He served as the Lead Independent Director of ION Geophysical Corporation since January 1, 2012 ... and has been its Director since 1998. He serves as a Director at Greater New Orleans Inc. He holds a Bachelor of Art in History from the University of Texas and Master of Business Administration and Juris Doctorate from Tulane University.Read Full Background




