Insider Activity


Individual




James Martial Lapeyre



Mr. James M. Lapeyre, Jr. MBA, is Chairman at Louisiana Association of Business & Industry, Chairman at ION Geophysical Corp., Chairman & President at Laitram LLC, and President at Intralox LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at Cato Institute, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Texas, a graduate degree from Tulane University (Louisiana), and an MBA from Tulane University (Louisiana).



