of $0.50 per share. As adjusted for the one-for-fifteen reverse stock split completed by ION on February 4, 2016, Laitram is authorized to purchase up to $3.0 million of ION Common Stock at a maximum gross sales price of $7.50 per share. As of
September 6, 2016, Laitram has purchased approximately $969,541 (excluding commissions) of ION Common Stock under the authorization. Other than as
described above or in the original Schedule 13Ds filed by The Laitram Corporation and Mr. Lapeyre or in any amendment thereto, neither Laitram nor, to the best of its knowledge, any of the persons named on Schedule A attached hereto has any plans or
